channel.title: :L Messed Up On Coding Need All New Commands
channel.description:
Well, Today, I Was Deleting Simple Commands And I Accidently Deleted "}" On One Of The Commands, And I Couldn't Find Witch So I Said..
F*** It, And Deleted All My Commands.
So Now I Need All The Simple Commands To Add Into Client.java.
Such As:
::message
::pickup
::xteleto
::xteletome
::xteleall
::banuser
::unbanuser
::jail
::unjail
::ipban
::mute
::unmute
::ipmute
::mod *To Give Someone Mod Ingame*
::admin *to Give Someone Admin Ingame*
::owner *To Give Someone Co-Owner (Owner) In Game*.
Thanks For The Help (:
